node.text:
@jacobandco with a true grand complication , the TWIN TURBO FURIOUS BAGUETTE WHITE DIAMONDS & TSAVORITES ROSE GOLD once again breaking traditional watch making rules with this masterpiece 

The Twin Turbo Furious takes the exceptionally cool and uniquely complex Twin Turbo concept and takes it to the next level by adding a Monopusher Chronograph and Pit Board time difference calculator to the original's twin triple-axis tourbillon and decimal minute repeater. With its painstakingly hand-decorated and hand-assembled 832 components, the Twin Turbo Furious is a true Grand Complication Masterpiece that offers a singular combination of ultra-high-end mechanisms, all exclusive to @jacobandco
